    Verse: 7
Tags:
  - Love
---
Without love one lacks the warmth and emotions which create life, youth
and beauty. He is like a stagnant pond compared with a flowing,
babbling, laughing brook. He depresses the life force in those around him
instead of radiating sunshine to all who come near him.
